in Markus's team back in the day.

118
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,959
And I've always had serious doubts

119
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,079
that she is the person responsible
for Shen Chuan's accident.

120
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:13,459
Really? Is she really Shen Chuan's sister?

121
00:07:13,459 --> 00:07:15,720
How does Ruifeng take responsibility
for quality and safety?

122
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,340
Is there anything you want
to explain about this matter?

123
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:18,540
Can you talk about it? Say something.

124
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:20,100
That is not today's topic.

125
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:22,800
All your explanations will turn into sophistry.

126
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,279
Wasn't Ruifeng aware of this?

127
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,079
To what extent are you guys short of staff?

128
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,016
No bearing of past grudges?

129
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,940
Can you promise that Ruifeng and Maituo

130
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:36,160
