Excuse me, are you Shen Xi?

132
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:39,340
Shen Chuan's sister?

133
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:41,240
You used to work for Markus, right?

134
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:44,120
[Ruifeng Press Conference]
Did your make a mistake, Engineer Shen,

135
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,279
