136
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:47,620
What were you thinking

137
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:49,079
when you became Chen Mobai's engineer?

138
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,519
You used to work at Markus, didn't you?

139
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,519
Why did you hide the truth
after returning to the country?

140
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:54,019
What were you thinking

141
00:07:54,019 --> 00:07:55,319
when you became Chen Mobai's engineer?

142
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:05,079
